WEBVTT

00:04.751 --> 00:12.998
Three hundred million years ago, there was no Africa, Asia, Americas or Europe.

00:14.489 --> 00:20.507
Just one, big supercontinent: pangaea.

00:22.055 --> 00:26.525
And today, there is still a force connecting those divided by distance,...

00:28.987 --> 00:31.537
...reversing millions of years of rifting.

00:36.929 --> 00:39.499
Making far feel close.

00:41.041 --> 00:43.135
Bringing there to here.

00:51.209 --> 00:52.433
Turkish Airlines.

